latestPosts.caption:
Of the Arts. Type 00 in French Ultramarine.
 
Embedded in French arts and culture since the Renaissance, Ultramarine Blue has long symbolised artistic mastery and those who defy convention. A natural choice for Type 00’s latest appearance.
 
Created in-house with a bespoke pigment and metallic content, its satin-like finish accentuates Type 00’s singular form.
